lead_paragraph: TRIAL TRIP OF THE U.S. PROPELLER, SAN JACINTO.--This vessel made a trip to the South-West Spit and back to the Navy Yard on Monday last. As far as regards her speed, we understand she performed satisfactorily; but there are many faults about her which will require correction. In truth, it is though by some that she is more than half a failure.
